Micah 5-5 <t>And he shall be <f>ⓛ</f>their peace. </t> <pb/><t><f>ⓜ</f>When the Assyrian comes into our land </t><t>and treads in our palaces, </t><t>then we will raise against him seven <f>ⓝ</f>shepherds </t><t>and eight princes of men;</t>
