Micah 5-8 <t>And <f>ⓡ</f>the remnant of Jacob shall be among the nations, </t><t>in the midst of many peoples, </t><t>like a lion among the beasts of the forest, </t><t>like a young lion among the flocks of sheep, </t><t><f>ⓢ</f>which, when it goes through, treads down </t><t>and tears in pieces, and there is none to deliver.</t>
